37  struct PredicateAccumulatorDefaultTrue {

39 
40  template <typename T_iterator>
41  result_type operator()( T_iterator first, T_iterator last ) const {

54  struct InterruptablePredicateAccumulatorDefaultFalse {

76  struct MessageHandlerAccumulator {
77  typedef HandlerResult result_type;
78 
79  template <typename T_iterator>
80  result_type operator()( T_iterator first, T_iterator last ) const {
81  HandlerResult retval = NOT_HANDLED;
82  while ( first != last ) {
83  switch ( *first )
84  {
85  case HANDLED:
86  return HANDLED;
87  case HANDLER_NEEDS_MEMORY:
88  retval = HANDLER_NEEDS_MEMORY;
89  // no break because we'll slide through to the next case
90  case NOT_HANDLED:
91  ++first;
92  }
93  }
94  return retval;
95  }
96  };
